{
  "stem": "1141.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And no matter what I said or did, they did not believe me that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told them, you can kill me, and I wish you would.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still don't know where she is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were going in the hay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they have one of these things that you stick-- it's like a fork.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were going there because they were under the impression that she was hiding underneath the hay, which some of them did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't-- I hate to tell you what happened to those people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were going down and trying to see if she is underneath the hay.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- no matter what I did, no matter how I pleaded with them, begging to shoot me, just I don't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just simply don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so they-- they just [INAUDIBLE] ugly guy from Oberschlesien who did this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put the bullets-- when they brought them out, they put a bullet straight into their head and just let them die there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't blame them from trying to-- trying to hide, because we didn't know where they're taking us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, where we wound up after Oberschlesien and Bergen-Belsen, that's where the real problems started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were prepared in Auschwitz and in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had the facilities all laid out, all planned out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen was not prepared for such-- so many people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when they brought a lot of people from all over to Bergen-Belsen, they contracted typhoid, including myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By trucks, by walking, by trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how long the trip took to get there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we got there, that was--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
